  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in the tajine clay vessel over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped carrots and celery and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the red chilli powder, dried thyme, and bay leaves and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the rinsed lentils, vegetable broth, and tomato paste, stirring to combine.",
    "Bring the stew to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the bay leaves and season the stew with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve the stew hot, garnished with fresh herbs if desired."
